{
    "publish_date": "2012-06-20T03:58:31.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT11M49S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "If you&#39;ve been watching the news lately,\nhave probably seen photographs like this.", 
            "dur": "4.051", 
            "start": "4.863"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Students are protesting", 
            "dur": "1.658", 
            "start": "8.914"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because their government is cutting\nsubsidies to education.", 
            "dur": "3.199", 
            "start": "10.572"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the big part of the reason for this,", 
            "dur": "2.057", 
            "start": "13.771"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "both the government cutting subsidies", 
            "dur": "1.978", 
            "start": "15.828"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and student now cry is that", 
            "dur": "1.901", 
            "start": "17.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "getting a college education\ndoesn&#39;t cost what it used to.", 
            "dur": "2.999", 
            "start": "19.757"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you graduated more than 2 decades ago,", 
            "dur": "2.058", 
            "start": "23.557"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you might be surprised to know that", 
            "dur": "1.724", 
            "start": "25.615"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it now costs students\nover two and a half times", 
            "dur": "2.43", 
            "start": "27.339"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as much as it did for you,", 
            "dur": "1.696", 
            "start": "29.769"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that&#39;s in real dollars\nfor any economists in the audience here.", 
            "dur": "3.578", 
            "start": "31.465"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s not an easy problem.", 
            "dur": "2.104", 
            "start": "35.043"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "On one hand\nthe cost is becoming harder for both,", 
            "dur": "2.4", 
            "start": "37.147"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "students and government to bare.", 
            "dur": "1.847", 
            "start": "39.547"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But in the other hand\nemployers are demanding", 
            "dur": "2.146", 
            "start": "41.394"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "an educated workforce.", 
            "dur": "1.442", 
            "start": "43.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They want employees\nwith complex analytical skills.", 
            "dur": "3.599", 
            "start": "44.982"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The world now runs\noot of what we dig out of people brains", 
            "dur": "3.367", 
            "start": "48.581"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not just what we dig out of the ground.", 
            "dur": "2.387", 
            "start": "51.948"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, that&#39;s the problem.", 
            "dur": "1.257", 
            "start": "56.351"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now what&#39;s the fix?", 
            "dur": "1.563", 
            "start": "57.608"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Let me be completely honest with you.", 
            "dur": "2.333", 
            "start": "59.171"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have no idea.", 
            "dur": "1.869", 
            "start": "61.504"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But what I want to suggest is that maybe\nwe&#39;ve been looking in the wrong place.", 
            "dur": "4.717", 
            "start": "63.373"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;ve been expecting change\nto come from schools and governments,", 
            "dur": "3.212", 
            "start": "68.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but what if the change came from us.", 
            "dur": "2.386", 
            "start": "71.302"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;d like to share my story\nand suggest that maybe", 
            "dur": "2.411", 
            "start": "74.982"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "an education doesn&#39;t need to be expensive", 
            "dur": "2.48", 
            "start": "77.403"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and what&#39;s more,", 
            "dur": "1.583", 
            "start": "79.883"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "maybe we can learn better without it.", 
            "dur": "2.048", 
            "start": "81.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So in my case I was lucky.", 
            "dur": "1.754", 
            "start": "83.514"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When I was accepted to college,", 
            "dur": "1.837", 
            "start": "85.268"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I managed to narrow down\nmy choice in major to two choices:", 
            "dur": "2.684", 
            "start": "87.105"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Business and computer science.", 
            "dur": "1.501", 
            "start": "89.789"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was really interested in both.", 
            "dur": "1.742", 
            "start": "91.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "With one you get to build companies,", 
            "dur": "1.741", 
            "start": "93.032"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with the other\nyou get to build technologies.", 
            "dur": "2.202", 
            "start": "94.773"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And these two are not mutually exclusive.", 
            "dur": "2.203", 
            "start": "96.975"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After all Bill Gates was a hacker\nbefore he built an empire. (Laughter)", 
            "dur": "3.52", 
            "start": "99.178"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But in my school\nI could only major in one.", 
            "dur": "2.646", 
            "start": "102.698"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I did what any freshman would do,", 
            "dur": "1.881", 
            "start": "105.387"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and did a careful rational\ncost-benefit analysis.", 
            "dur": "2.616", 
            "start": "107.268"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Gender Ratio]\n(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "3.918", 
            "start": "109.884"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So business it was, and after graduating", 
            "dur": "2.177", 
            "start": "113.802"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have no regrets.", 
            "dur": "2.836", 
            "start": "115.979"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I learned a lot and I had a great time.", 
            "dur": "2.619", 
            "start": "118.815"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But after finishing my education,", 
            "dur": "2.08", 
            "start": "122.211"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had this longing for the path not taken.", 
            "dur": "2.23", 
            "start": "124.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I really wanted to learn computer science.", 
            "dur": "2.111", 
            "start": "126.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But going back to school\ndidn&#39;t appeal to me", 
            "dur": "3.167", 
            "start": "128.651"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "four more years of my life,", 
            "dur": "1.398", 
            "start": "131.818"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "acceptance boards, tuition bills,", 
            "dur": "1.607", 
            "start": "133.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I didn&#39;t want to postpone my life\nand rack up debt,", 
            "dur": "2.865", 
            "start": "134.823"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just to pursue a curiosity.", 
            "dur": "2.554", 
            "start": "137.688"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I wanted the education, not the school.", 
            "dur": "2.812", 
            "start": "140.242"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then I remembered that\nUniversities like MIT, Harvard, Stanford,", 
            "dur": "3.869", 
            "start": "143.408"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "had a habit of putting up classes\nonline for free.", 
            "dur": "2.794", 
            "start": "148.164"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve done a few of these before\nand then a thought occurred to me.", 
            "dur": "3.045", 
            "start": "150.958"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you could learn a class,\nwhy not an entire degree.", 
            "dur": "3.076", 
            "start": "154.003"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That was the beginning of an experiment.", 
            "dur": "2.009", 
            "start": "158.288"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Would it be possible to get\nan MIT education in computer science", 
            "dur": "3.876", 
            "start": "160.297"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "without ever going to MIT?", 
            "dur": "2.683", 
            "start": "164.355"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So it&#39;s an intriguing idea,", 
            "dur": "2.292", 
            "start": "167.169"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but already you could probably notice", 
            "dur": "1.78", 
            "start": "169.461"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the complexities and objections\nthat may raise", 
            "dur": "2.366", 
            "start": "171.241"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so going to the MIT is a lot more\nthan just what you learn in the classroom.", 
            "dur": "3.433", 
            "start": "173.607"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So how can you possibly hope\nto replicate something", 
            "dur": "2.773", 
            "start": "177.04"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which is such a multifaceted experience.", 
            "dur": "2.259", 
            "start": "179.831"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I like to think college is a lot", 
            "dur": "2.595", 
            "start": "182.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like eating at a five star restaurant.", 
            "dur": "1.997", 
            "start": "184.685"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re never paying for just the food.", 
            "dur": "1.978", 
            "start": "186.682"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You get the wait staff, elegant decor,\nthe fancy french wines.", 
            "dur": "4.064", 
            "start": "188.737"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re paying for a complex\nand multifaceted experience.", 
            "dur": "3.212", 
            "start": "192.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the same is true at college.", 
            "dur": "1.955", 
            "start": "196.162"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You get networking\nwith your intellectual peers,", 
            "dur": "2.302", 
            "start": "198.117"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "research opportunities\nand credentials from elite institutions.", 
            "dur": "2.662", 
            "start": "200.419"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And like the fancy restaurant", 
            "dur": "1.965", 
            "start": "203.081"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you get a big bill at the end.", 
            "dur": "1.953", 
            "start": "205.046"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you know what,\nsometimes this system works,", 
            "dur": "2.29", 
            "start": "208.702"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but just as you probably don&#39;t want\nto go to a five star restaurant,", 
            "dur": "3.056", 
            "start": "210.992"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "every time you get hungry,", 
            "dur": "1.569", 
            "start": "214.048"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you probably also\ndon&#39;t want to go back to school", 
            "dur": "2.204", 
            "start": "215.617"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "every time you want to learn something.", 
            "dur": "2.07", 
            "start": "217.821"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I didn&#39;t want the five course meal.", 
            "dur": "1.836", 
            "start": "219.891"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I wanted my education &quot;a la carte&quot;.", 
            "dur": "2.698", 
            "start": "221.727"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So what mattered most to me, \nwas being able to understand", 
            "dur": "2.601", 
            "start": "225.333"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the big ideas of computer science;", 
            "dur": "1.765", 
            "start": "227.934"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like algorithms, artificial intelligence,", 
            "dur": "1.982", 
            "start": "229.699"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "encryption, and the Internet.", 
            "dur": "1.508", 
            "start": "231.789"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And being able to implement those ideas\nin computer programs.", 
            "dur": "3.381", 
            "start": "233.297"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I decided to make my challenge simple.", 
            "dur": "2.206", 
            "start": "237.849"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My goal will be to try to pass the exams\nan MIT student would do", 
            "dur": "3.856", 
            "start": "240.055"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and to do the programming projects.", 
            "dur": "1.958", 
            "start": "243.921"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I admit it is a simplification.", 
            "dur": "1.657", 
            "start": "245.879"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It omits a lot of the MIT experiences.", 
            "dur": "2.109", 
            "start": "247.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But for what I wanted to get out of it,", 
            "dur": "2.279", 
            "start": "249.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it was a pretty good simplification.", 
            "dur": "2.012", 
            "start": "252.009"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And what mattered more,", 
            "dur": "1.309", 
            "start": "254.021"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it was a simplification that worked.", 
            "dur": "1.982", 
            "start": "255.33"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I was able\nto build a curriculum of 33 classes,", 
            "dur": "3.16", 
            "start": "257.312"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that with one or two minor exceptions", 
            "dur": "2.287", 
            "start": "260.472"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was identical to the course list\nan MIT student would use.", 
            "dur": "2.797", 
            "start": "262.759"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I was able to build this using only\nMIT&#39;s free online available information.", 
            "dur": "5.28", 
            "start": "266.828"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The only cost was for a few text books", 
            "dur": "3.102", 
            "start": "272.95"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which meant I could follow\nthis entire program for under $2000.", 
            "dur": "5.652", 
            "start": "276.052"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I had my goal\nand now I have the material.", 
            "dur": "3.103", 
            "start": "281.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now for the hard part:\nactually learning MIT classes.", 
            "dur": "3.112", 
            "start": "285.103"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m not kidding myself,\nMIT is a really hard school", 
            "dur": "2.459", 
            "start": "288.415"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s notoriously difficult\neven for bright students", 
            "dur": "2.511", 
            "start": "291.043"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and what is more, I&#39;m not going to have\nthe help of faculty,", 
            "dur": "3.043", 
            "start": "293.692"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and professors, and classmates\nthat I can easily get help from.", 
            "dur": "4.007", 
            "start": "296.735"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In theory the project&#39;s doable\nbut it was too difficult in practice.", 
            "dur": "5.127", 
            "start": "300.788"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When I told my friends about this,", 
            "dur": "2.82", 
            "start": "305.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I was planning on doing\nan MIT degree on my own,", 
            "dur": "2.469", 
            "start": "308.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they reinforced those doubts.", 
            "dur": "1.438", 
            "start": "311.205"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They told me they could not imagine", 
            "dur": "1.734", 
            "start": "312.643"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "trying to learn a MIT degree on your own.", 
            "dur": "2.131", 
            "start": "314.377"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;d be too difficult without constant\nguidance and support of faculty members.", 
            "dur": "4.614", 
            "start": "316.508"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But that last point\ndidn&#39;t ring true for me,", 
            "dur": "2.692", 
            "start": "321.368"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because when I went to college,\nI was in lecture halls like this one,", 
            "dur": "3.146", 
            "start": "324.06"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where the professor would give a talk", 
            "dur": "1.698", 
            "start": "327.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to an auditorium full of 300 students.", 
            "dur": "1.755", 
            "start": "328.904"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yeah, sure that if I had a question\nI could rise my hand,", 
            "dur": "3.347", 
            "start": "330.675"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but if really didn&#39;t understand something", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "334.027"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it was up to me to learn it", 
            "dur": "1.563", 
            "start": "336.087"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so perhaps the doubts and worries\nover do-it-yourself degree,", 
            "dur": "4.228", 
            "start": "337.65"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "had more to do\nwith it being unconventional,", 
            "dur": "2.496", 
            "start": "342.155"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "than it being genuinely more difficult\nthan a formal program.", 
            "dur": "3.178", 
            "start": "344.651"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As I started doing the first few classes,", 
            "dur": "2.374", 
            "start": "348.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "my results were even more surprising.", 
            "dur": "2.373", 
            "start": "351.01"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I found I was able to learn faster\nusing this approach", 
            "dur": "2.741", 
            "start": "353.453"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "than I ever had while in university.", 
            "dur": "2.293", 
            "start": "356.215"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So far from being an obstacle,", 
            "dur": "1.93", 
            "start": "358.508"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it turned out that not going to MIT", 
            "dur": "1.759", 
            "start": "360.438"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "had made my job a lot easier.", 
            "dur": "2.083", 
            "start": "362.197"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ok, so that last bit\ndeserves a little bit of explanation.", 
            "dur": "3.71", 
            "start": "364.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After all, an MIT student has access\nto everything I do, and much much more.", 
            "dur": "4.696", 
            "start": "367.995"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How can I possibly have an advantage\nover a student", 
            "dur": "3.013", 
            "start": "372.691"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when I have a fewer resources?", 
            "dur": "1.565", 
            "start": "375.708"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It defies common sense.", 
            "dur": "1.556", 
            "start": "377.299"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So in order to explain this,\nI need to do a little bit of a detour.", 
            "dur": "3.698", 
            "start": "378.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I need to go into the geeky realm\nof personal productivity.", 
            "dur": "3.414", 
            "start": "382.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So there is a tool called the time log.", 
            "dur": "2.345", 
            "start": "385.973"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And here is how the time log works.", 
            "dur": "2.167", 
            "start": "388.318"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You jot down the starting\nand the stopping times", 
            "dur": "2.473", 
            "start": "390.485"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for every activity you do.", 
            "dur": "2.263", 
            "start": "392.958"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I mean every activity,\nfrom when you wake up in the morning,", 
            "dur": "3.125", 
            "start": "395.221"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to when you take out the garbage.", 
            "dur": "1.525", 
            "start": "398.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My guess is that most of you here\nhave never done a time log before,", 
            "dur": "3.622", 
            "start": "399.871"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because just imagine\nhow irritating that is to do.", 
            "dur": "2.746", 
            "start": "403.493"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But if you do one,\nthe results can be eye-opening.", 
            "dur": "3.2", 
            "start": "406.239"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here&#39;s a recent\nWall Street Journal article", 
            "dur": "2.298", 
            "start": "409.439"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where the reporter did just that.", 
            "dur": "2.094", 
            "start": "411.737"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She writes:", 
            "dur": "1.383", 
            "start": "413.831"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;I soon realized I&#39;d been lying to myself", 
            "dur": "1.935", 
            "start": "415.214"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about where the time was going.", 
            "dur": "1.643", 
            "start": "417.149"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What I thought was a 60-hour workweek\nwasn&#39;t even close.", 
            "dur": "3.169", 
            "start": "418.792"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would have guessed I spent hours\ndoing dishes when in fact", 
            "dur": "2.82", 
            "start": "421.961"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I spent minutes.", 
            "dur": "1.069", 
            "start": "424.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I spent long stretches of time\nlost on the Internet", 
            "dur": "2.604", 
            "start": "425.865"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or puttering around the house,\nunsure exactly what I was doing.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.443", 
            "start": "428.469"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because I am huge geek\nI&#39;ve done time logs before", 
            "dur": "3.147", 
            "start": "431.912"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I can say\nthe situation is even worse for students.", 
            "dur": "2.557", 
            "start": "435.059"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The vast majority of time students spend,", 
            "dur": "2.377", 
            "start": "437.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "isn&#39;t spent learning,\nit&#39;s spent commuting to class,", 
            "dur": "2.438", 
            "start": "439.993"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "copying notes at Starbucks,\nand trying to stay awake in lectures.", 
            "dur": "5.026", 
            "start": "442.431"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you could total up the amount of time", 
            "dur": "2.521", 
            "start": "447.457"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that students spend forming new insight,", 
            "dur": "2.334", 
            "start": "449.978"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and remembering facts which is of course", 
            "dur": "1.916", 
            "start": "452.312"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what learning is, it would be tiny.", 
            "dur": "2.259", 
            "start": "454.228"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And for the most part,\nthis is not even the student&#39;s fault.", 
            "dur": "2.63", 
            "start": "456.487"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After all, entrepreneurs often notice", 
            "dur": "2.072", 
            "start": "459.117"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a startling difference\nin their productivity,", 
            "dur": "2.121", 
            "start": "461.189"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at a start-up versus a big firm.", 
            "dur": "1.773", 
            "start": "463.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Big institutions mean bureaucracy.", 
            "dur": "1.324", 
            "start": "465.083"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They mean paper work,\nthey mean doing what you&#39;re told", 
            "dur": "2.686", 
            "start": "466.407"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "instead of what&#39;s important.", 
            "dur": "1.676", 
            "start": "469.093"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So being an educational entrepreneur\ncan offer some learning advantages", 
            "dur": "4.532", 
            "start": "470.769"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "over people in a formal system.", 
            "dur": "2.019", 
            "start": "475.301"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, take lectures as a perfect example", 
            "dur": "2.646", 
            "start": "477.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, when I would do MIT lectures,\nwhen I started doing the classes,", 
            "dur": "3.392", 
            "start": "479.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would watch them\nat one and a half times the speed.", 
            "dur": "2.721", 
            "start": "483.558"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This may sound very difficult,\nbut the difference", 
            "dur": "2.95", 
            "start": "486.487"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is barely audible in human speech,", 
            "dur": "2.023", 
            "start": "489.468"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if it goes too fast, you just hit rewind.", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "491.491"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Students in a regular classroom\ndon&#39;t have access", 
            "dur": "3.189", 
            "start": "494.219"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to a fast-forward or rewind button,", 
            "dur": "2.275", 
            "start": "497.412"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even though I&#39;m guessing\nmost of them would like one.", 
            "dur": "2.461", 
            "start": "499.687"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the impact of this isn&#39;t trivial.", 
            "dur": "1.979", 
            "start": "502.148"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "By being able to watch lectures\nat a slightly faster pace,", 
            "dur": "2.716", 
            "start": "504.127"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and watching them sequentially,", 
            "dur": "1.685", 
            "start": "506.843"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was able to take classes\nthat normally span four months,", 
            "dur": "3.143", 
            "start": "508.528"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and watch them in two days of real time.", 
            "dur": "2.283", 
            "start": "511.671"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or take assignments.", 
            "dur": "2.294", 
            "start": "513.954"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Students do assignments\nbecause they have to.", 
            "dur": "2.284", 
            "start": "516.248"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yes, sometimes they facilitate learning,", 
            "dur": "2.117", 
            "start": "518.532"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but sometimes they don&#39;t.", 
            "dur": "1.257", 
            "start": "520.649"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "For example,\nif you are struggling with a concept", 
            "dur": "2.468", 
            "start": "521.922"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "why wait weeks to get your answers back?", 
            "dur": "2.099", 
            "start": "524.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When I would do a hard MIT assignment,", 
            "dur": "1.991", 
            "start": "526.489"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would do the questions\nwith the solution key in hand,", 
            "dur": "2.573", 
            "start": "528.49"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "one question at a time,", 
            "dur": "1.686", 
            "start": "531.063"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because it&#39;s tight feedback loops\nlike this", 
            "dur": "2.456", 
            "start": "532.749"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that cognitive scientists recognize\nas being critical to learning.", 
            "dur": "3.053", 
            "start": "535.205"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you don&#39;t need to be a genius\nto apply these ideas either.", 
            "dur": "2.785", 
            "start": "538.258"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "being able to replay\nkeys segments of lectures;", 
            "dur": "2.251", 
            "start": "541.043"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "being able to get\nimmediate feedback on your skills;", 
            "dur": "2.429", 
            "start": "543.294"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "these are structural advantages\nthat benefit slow learners", 
            "dur": "2.779", 
            "start": "545.723"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as much as they benefit fast ones.", 
            "dur": "1.888", 
            "start": "548.502"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, where am I right now?", 
            "dur": "2.363", 
            "start": "550.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As of this moment I&#39;ve completed 20\nof the 33 computer science courses", 
            "dur": "4.971", 
            "start": "553.092"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in the MIT curriculum.", 
            "dur": "1.791", 
            "start": "558.078"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And by completed I mean", 
            "dur": "1.453", 
            "start": "559.885"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve passed those final exams\nand I did the programing projects", 
            "dur": "3.147", 
            "start": "561.354"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "associated with those classes.", 
            "dur": "2.036", 
            "start": "564.501"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What&#39;s more, because of speed-ups\nlike this that I have mentioned,", 
            "dur": "3.05", 
            "start": "566.537"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m on track of finishing the program\nin 12 months instead of 4 years.", 
            "dur": "4.371", 
            "start": "569.609"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So today the big topic is about\nhow technology is going to change", 
            "dur": "3.584", 
            "start": "576.072"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "educational institutions and classrooms.", 
            "dur": "2.854", 
            "start": "579.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think this misses the point.", 
            "dur": "2.284", 
            "start": "582.517"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The big upheavals in education\naren&#39;t going to be about schools,", 
            "dur": "3.57", 
            "start": "584.801"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They are going to be about students.", 
            "dur": "1.967", 
            "start": "588.371"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I am not alone in believing this.", 
            "dur": "1.932", 
            "start": "590.338"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There is already grassroot organizations", 
            "dur": "2.116", 
            "start": "592.285"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "looking to rethink education,\nnot from the top-down", 
            "dur": "2.673", 
            "start": "594.401"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but from the bottom-up.", 
            "dur": "1.764", 
            "start": "597.074"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "These are movements that\nare not planned by schools or governments,", 
            "dur": "3.096", 
            "start": "598.838"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but from students who are fed up\nwith the limited options", 
            "dur": "2.593", 
            "start": "601.934"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the current system provides.", 
            "dur": "1.786", 
            "start": "604.558"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Education hacking is the new trend.", 
            "dur": "2.975", 
            "start": "606.381"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So billionaire investor Peter Thiel gives\n100,000 dollar scholarship to students,", 
            "dur": "5.091", 
            "start": "609.424"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not to go to school but to drop out,\nand start something interesting.", 
            "dur": "3.951", 
            "start": "614.515"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So when the best and brightest and\nmost motivated start singling their talent", 
            "dur": "4.389", 
            "start": "618.774"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by not going to school,\nthe rest of the world will take notice.", 
            "dur": "3.975", 
            "start": "623.163"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it is not an &quot;all or nothing&quot;\nproposition either.", 
            "dur": "2.5", 
            "start": "627.415"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Jay Cross,\nthe founder of &quot;Do-It-Yourself Degree&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.335", 
            "start": "629.915"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is putting together\na list of universities", 
            "dur": "2.031", 
            "start": "632.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "based on the number of transfers credits\nthey accept.", 
            "dur": "2.447", 
            "start": "634.281"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That means you can go\nto a real university,", 
            "dur": "2.137", 
            "start": "636.728"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and get a real degree,", 
            "dur": "1.457", 
            "start": "638.865"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but minimize the amount of time\nyou have to spend", 
            "dur": "2.47", 
            "start": "640.322"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "learning in the classroom.", 
            "dur": "2.47", 
            "start": "642.792"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Look, I get it,\nmaybe you don&#39;t want to go to MIT", 
            "dur": "2.47", 
            "start": "645.262"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or try to learn an MIT degree on your own\njust for fun, I get that.", 
            "dur": "3.73", 
            "start": "647.732"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But even if you decide\nto do your education the old fashion way,", 
            "dur": "4.016", 
            "start": "651.462"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this still impacts you.", 
            "dur": "1.717", 
            "start": "655.478"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The world is changing too fast\nto believe that learning stops", 
            "dur": "2.909", 
            "start": "657.195"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "once you get your diploma.", 
            "dur": "1.731", 
            "start": "660.104"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Being able to teach yourself\ncomplex skills and big ideas", 
            "dur": "3.899", 
            "start": "661.835"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is going to be essential to stay ahead.", 
            "dur": "2.503", 
            "start": "665.734"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, like it or not,\nmost education in the future", 
            "dur": "3.039", 
            "start": "668.237"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is going to be self-education.", 
            "dur": "2.509", 
            "start": "671.276"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Universities aren&#39;t going away\nanytime soon,", 
            "dur": "2.731", 
            "start": "673.785"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they will always offer things\nself-education will miss.", 
            "dur": "2.772", 
            "start": "676.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They&#39;re a great experience", 
            "dur": "2.165", 
            "start": "679.288"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even if they&#39;re sometimes\nan expensive one.", 
            "dur": "2.109", 
            "start": "681.453"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But that said,\nI believe self-education is the future.", 
            "dur": "3.266", 
            "start": "683.562"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If a person like me can learn\nan MIT degree in one quarter of the time", 
            "dur": "4.052", 
            "start": "687.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and 1/100 of the financial cost,", 
            "dur": "2.985", 
            "start": "691.358"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what&#39;s to stop you from doing it too?", 
            "dur": "2.578", 
            "start": "694.343"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thank you.", 
            "dur": "1.524", 
            "start": "696.921"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": "1.253", 
            "start": "698.445"
        }
    ], 
